{"tid":461024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲今日宣佈台灣將成為該國入境「智慧閘門」永久適用國  可享快速通關禮遇","createTime":"2017-11-07T07:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T14:47:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"7be2d98227968ee1c76cdafec13051b61ab369e2","tid":461024,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"台灣民眾再在國際上再獲得禮遇！繼早前被納入美國的「全球入境計劃（Global Entry）」，持台灣民眾不用排長龍，可持護照自助通關後，澳洲今日宣佈台灣將成為該國入境「智慧閘門」（Arrivals SmartGate）的永久適用國，今日起，台灣民眾不用事前登記申請，便可在澳洲各主要國際機場，自助入境。<br />\n<br />\n只要年滿16歲、持有中華民國晶片護照的台灣民眾，便可以使用「智慧閘門」通關，台灣的外交部指，此舉將幅增進台灣民眾前往澳洲商旅的便利性，有利台灣和澳洲出入境人士互訪，深化雙方實質交流與合作。<br />\n<br />\n不過，台灣民眾入境前需上網申請「電子旅行簽證」（Electronic Travel Authority，簡稱ETA），方能出發前往澳洲；大陸的民眾前往澳洲，不但需要申請簽證，而且到埗後要排隊，等候邊檢人員檢查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171107/57429064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171107%2F57429064&d=uRLXyxrl2rCmh2DUqYmbWpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=37808798\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171107%2F57429064&h=9e1b0b84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171107/57429064</a>"},{"pid":"bc7ba5413f020bf3d433bb6d3cf0982ee192bf7c","tid":461024,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:37:06.000Z","msg":"一樣要網上簽證"},{"pid":"c07194198a57814ea3562b710016c96193f3f8e1","tid":461024,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"香港？"},{"pid":"84d0a6039728bec579fe4e5867c4caa2e7a0bdcb","tid":461024,"uid":33653,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n排啦"},{"pid":"7221ba31b184fb6cdd91c055c17ec4f57bfd09c7","tid":461024,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一樣要網上簽證</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n澳洲全部都要網簽"},{"pid":"4db49a22b0fafce1f090cfc1c342efa35c8efbf6","tid":461024,"uid":16970,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"求依個post見到&quot;民國復興&quot;用戶嘅機會率?"},{"pid":"bbde0aaa03eb10af17b2ae724078bfe5c2e8c1d3","tid":461024,"uid":21873,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港？</blockquote><br />\n香港護照中國都好易拎到，係都比bno啦"},{"pid":"2b8e41626e7a9d84e7aef03c26b19e65092f2019","tid":461024,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"支那用到澳洲smart gate"},{"pid":"e18626dde30f669c32518fd26f8cbbe06369f91a","tid":461024,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:41:38.000Z","msg":"又唔認台灣係獨立國家<br />\n但又俾台灣咁多優惠<br />\n班鬼佬想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢2家茶禮真係易食"},{"pid":"ee63001e365d723fef94c1d9ff5afb02f8a7f5bd","tid":461024,"uid":22218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港？</blockquote><br />\n香港護照中國都好易拎到，係都比bno啦</blockquote><br />\nbno 連自己上網做eta都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954dac0d7a019232d13d6a58018018e820f01141","tid":461024,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港？</blockquote><br />\n特衰用到，BNO都得"},{"pid":"800d0da065bf8806c5253060783b62a8c5d68976","tid":461024,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港？</blockquote><br />\n特衰用到，BNO都得</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9936a18c609bd6f5a994e0217ce55fc36c4e4f34","tid":461024,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07