要去旅行社搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b56ed6efd56c4e4175e17b8544e6c101b2fbc2","tid":461024,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又唔認台灣係獨立國家<br />\n但又俾台灣咁多優惠<br />\n班鬼佬想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢2家茶禮真係易食</blockquote><br />\n你覺得點解呢"},{"pid":"d5738aa4fe472112010594171b12270367372b84","tid":461024,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又唔認台灣係獨立國家<br />\n但又俾台灣咁多優惠<br />\n班鬼佬想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢2家茶禮真係易食</blockquote><br />\n你覺得點解呢</blockquote><br />\n入境優待明明係privilege，其實唔明咩心態會覺得係「想食兩家茶禮」"},{"pid":"03fa01e6e554ef4e6822e4f587493a0e9bd1e0ed","tid":461024,"uid":80028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:37:57.000Z","msg":"You are eligible to use arrivals SmartGate if you:<br />\n<br />\nare aged 16 years* or older<br />\nhold an ePassport from one of the following:<br />\nAustralia<br />\nCanada<br />\nChina<br />\nFrance<br />\nHong Kong<br />\nIreland<br />\nJapan<br />\nKorea<br />\nMacau<br />\nNew Zealand<br />\nSingapore<br />\nSweden<br />\nSwitzerland<br />\nUnited Kingdom<br />\nUnited States of America.<br />\nAirline crew who meet these eligibility requirements can choose to use arrivals SmartGate rather than being manually processed through the crew lane.<br />\nAustralian and New Zealand ePassport holders travelling on military orders are not eligible to use arrivals SmartGate.<br />\n* Australian children aged 10 to 15 years (inclusive) can use arrivals SmartGate if they are accompanied by at least two adults."},{"pid":"4503511bacfc9b88b5e2a7c8c4d4801ca642f373","tid":461024,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又唔認台灣係獨立國家<br />\n但又俾台灣咁多優惠<br />\n班鬼佬想點<i